{
  "stem": "10478.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the daughter, Toni, and the son, Fritz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that made me more or less active in finding a hiding place for-- for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I found a hiding place for the mother, the daughter in a grocery store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I knew also members of our church in Haelen, about 30 kilometers from Maastricht.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And but for him, for Fritz I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his mother begged me to find something for [INAUDIBLE] him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked my mother, I says, OK that Fritz comes for a couple of days at our place until I find a place for him?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my parents agreed to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Fritz came to our place for three or four days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, my mom said, ah, he's such a nice fellow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let him stay here, and we don't have to go anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Fritz stayed at our place until the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And through Fritz, I got more connections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His-- his cousin was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was released from the hospital and needed a place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found also a place for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He brought me in contact with his uncle and his wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And slowly on, like a snowball, more and more people approached me for finding a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was 22 years of age, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt obliged to find a place for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the consequences were if you couldn't find a place, they would end up in camp, and might-- might be killed, or murdered, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It came from our vision in our church that we had to help those people who were in need.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- we always felt-- was very sympathetic to the Jewish people for the simple reason we studied the Old Testament.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
